Detailed Description

cvmx_l2c_bst_mem#

L2C_BST_MEM = L2C MEM BIST Status

Notes: (1) CLEAR_BIST must be written to 1 before START_BIST is written to 1 using a separate CSR write.

(2) CLEAR_BIST must not be changed after writing START_BIST to 1 until the BIST operation completes (indicated by START_BIST returning to 0) or operation is undefined.
